  "title": "Pan-Seared Peppery Malaysian Fernbrake-Gosari Wrap",
  "description": "A spicy and savory Malaysian-inspired dish featuring pan-seared fernbrake-gosari in a pandan leaf wrap, served with a side of score-fat and ayurvedic-tamasic-friendly garnishes.",
  "cuisine": "Malaysian",
